feel her on my skin,

273
00:12:42,073 --> 00:12:43,947
nourish her,

274
00:12:44,031 --> 00:12:45,514
bond with her,

275
00:12:45,598 --> 00:12:48,110
and then you can take me.

276
00:12:50,429 --> 00:12:51,651
Of course.

277
00:12:51,735 --> 00:12:54,943
We'll give it a few more hours,
