appendix has fully ruptured.

455
00:20:15,656 --> 00:20:17,139
That's good.

456
00:20:17,223 --> 00:20:19,471
But I still can't get
a visual.

457
00:20:20,705 --> 00:20:22,144
I don't know.

458
00:20:22,228 --> 00:20:24,320
It's like the appendix isn't
